{"title":"谁怕谁？","authors":["飞花"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":8,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁怕谁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纳迪亚被判死刑！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是人民怕侯赛因，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是侯赛因怕人民？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侯赛因躲进深宫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不敢接见任何人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对自己的卫士也不信任。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纳迪亚在法庭受审，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她说她要炸毁王宫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要她能够走近。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侯赛因马上下令："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把所有妇女的手提包"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都给我一个个地搜寻！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界传来抗议的吼声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不许杀害纳迪亚！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侯赛因慌忙再下令："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没收全国收音机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切广播不许收听，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁违法要谁的命！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全球的抗议响如雷鸣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吓得侯赛因牙齿乱碰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被迫撤销了死刑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到底是谁怕谁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是人民怕暴君，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是猴崽子怕人？（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侯赛因和纳迪亚　　　英韬制"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}